    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-8075-a163-ee592ce7748e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "LMS and Learning Analytics have made it possible to pinpoint and identify potentially dilatory behavior from learners such as procrastination. Authors attempt to use ML to predict procrastinatory behavior by comparing 2 different feature sets:",
